author: The Spiffing Brit
description:
Welcome to Jurassic World Evolution 3 the latest game from frontier the creators of planet coaster and planet zoo! Some of the greatest tycoon park building games on the market. Today I am attempting to see how much money I can make in game whilst also feeding as many living human guests to my dinosaurs as possible! There is only one way to find out! And thats by watching the stream! 

This lovely event is sponsored by the developers and if you like the look of the game you can click on this link here to learn more: https://fron.dev/thespiffingbrit-jwe3

Also thanks to the developers for making this a challenge as I am actually competing against 3 Irish Creators!
